---
description: Supabase and database conventions
globs: lib/supabase/**/*.{ts,tsx},supabase/**/*,database/**/*,types/database.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

Follow `DATABASE_GUIDELINES.md`.

- RLS on all tables.
- Migrations in `supabase/migrations/`.
- Browser client: `lib/supabase/client.ts`.
- Server client: `lib/supabase/server.ts`.
- Admin client: `lib/supabase/admin.ts` (server only).
